query:
INSERT INTO pm_conversations (
                id, project_id, role, content, model
            ) VALUES (
                $1, $2, $3, $4, $5
            )
            RETURNING
                id as "id!: Uuid",
                project_id as "project_id!: Uuid",
                role,
                content,
                model,
                created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>",
                updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
